png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b442ffbd6a4aa76e69f88d46af9800cb8c7071","tid":1954573,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890f4d78176c08364ba095d9a1d6a652b13637b2","tid":1954573,"uid":349803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a60ad83e4d99de983733835785766daa8f56ab1","tid":1954573,"uid":84394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"真心狗<br />\n引傻仔賣樓買滙豐<br />\n唱好滙豐唱淡樓市<br />\n自己就沽滙豐買樓<br />\n真係祝佢早日負資產"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"香港有咁多on9跟專家買,點會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f90bbd8f11aa13f75b0c255ee868b0b06c538df","tid":1954573,"uid":344160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cdc97bf4facb84bffa01a76bc2b461d219726a9","tid":1954573,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"滙豐罕有地宣布不派息，市場嘩然，更令一眾股民心碎，向來熱衷於發表樓市言論的紀惠集團行政總裁湯文亮一八年發表言論，指滙豐可於三年內升至一百五十元，其後在其專欄指，有人看他的文章後「棄樓買滙豐」。此事昨日被人重提，湯文亮為此解畫：「純粹虛構故事。」<br />\n<br />\n滙豐對不起香港人<br />\n<br />\n就滙豐不派息，湯文亮昨日在社交網站回應：「有人叫我評論滙豐，簡單一句，滙豐對不起香港人。」「我為滙豐捱了一刀，大家應該明白，滙豐的管理層就算可以過得別人，都唔可以過得自己。」<br />\n<br />\n湯文亮曾於一八年三月三十日在專欄說，他為一對夫婦解決難題，他們打算以二千萬買樓自住，但認為樓價太高，看到其文章，指滙豐可於三年內升至一百五十元，於是將買樓首期連印花稅大約一千二百萬，全部買入滙豐，並與業主續三年租約，由於收取滙豐股息足夠交租，又不用供樓，兩公婆發短訊多謝他。<br />\n<br />\n網民昨日炮轟湯畀「山埃貼士」，Kelly昨日就這宗「棄樓買股」事件向湯查詢，他回應指：「這是虛構故事，不用介懷！」<br />\n<br />\n他更在社交網站回應指：「投資的事，千祈唔好睇返轉頭，否則會長在後悔中，自己投資是自己負責，去年我收到消息，話政府會取消買家印花稅（BSD），於是賣走一百萬股滙豐，以個人名義購入一個七千萬的住宅，消息後來證實BSD流料，我有多少後悔，現在當然不會，不過我仍持有一些滙豐，始終有多少耿耿於懷。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"仆街冚家剷"},{"pid":"32739d394364d573ae8e6f04b07b410ea4c76090","tid":1954573,"uid":260991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa264b24e46ea29ed2f26f1e27cbdc8f03e50c4","tid":1954573,"uid":275391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"收到消息取消印花稅偷步買樓，呢單野需唔需要廉署介入"},{"pid":"9cb28d1185f781570e8947f1715ef4f7fbf7d938","tid":1954573,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"下次佢燈啲文出嚟，即刻回一句係唔係虛構"},{"pid":"ba55e77a678c569426746df765f12e7f34618573","tid":1954573,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以告佢話佢故意製造虛假消息散播謠言，企圖影響匯豐當時股價？"},{"pid":"3fcd5950dc09ef3e10f0ead96bf1708a48b175c4","tid":1954573,"uid":133375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"專家食屎啦.jpg"},{"pid":"b7e9537712afc71e85efe0bb205401fbeac549ed","tid":1954573,"uid":60219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"睡得很甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果籃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n菲傭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e494afbcd0cb9e6d174a8834ee149e63e7c3a99b","tid":1954573,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"日日上fb留言「純粹虛構」<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1629532d6a746535a2edffb26e2a357f12d9f07","tid":1954573,"uid":177736,"like